nc_ohc=bNYj7K-JaF8Q7kNvgGOj0q7&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A28ihP_PQnD6Mw6VWWURi-V&oh=00_AYBElvbMdaiFGz-Fo5-Pm43gWNhKId2UT9fta_HaKqKxgw&oe=66E03279"}, "display_name": "Attack on Titan VR: Unbreakable", "keywords": ["AttackonTitan", "AoT", "Shingeki", "Action", "Hunting"], "long_description": "Fight for your life against man-eating Titans in Attack on Titan VR: Unbreakable. In a thrilling mix of hunting and action, join the Scout Regiment and put on your Omni Directional Mobility Gear to defend and protect humanity against the Titans. \n\nFeatures:\n\nExhilarating Flight Experience: Get ready for a unique adventure with UNIVRS\u2019 anti-motion sickness technology that will help bring the thrilling cross-range combat against killer Titans to life.\n\nMultiplayer: Team up with another member of the Scout Regiment in two-player co-op or go solo in the fight for humanity. \n\nDevise a strategy: There will be a number of enemies out to get you. With a wider range of weapons at your disposal, devise and execute the best plan to cut down the Titan population in the city.\n\n\u00a9 Hajime Isayama / Kodansha Ltd.   \u00a9 UNIVRS, Inc.", "short_description": "Fight for your life against man-eating Titans in Attack on Titan VR: Unbreakable. In a thrilling mix of hunting and action, join the Scout Regiment and put on your Omni Directional Mobility Gear to defend and protect humanity against the Titans. \n\n\u00a9 Hajime Isayama / Kodansha Ltd.   \u00a9 UNIVRS, Inc."}]}, "developer_name": "UNIVRS, Inc.", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://univrs.jp/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "UNIVRS, Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://aotvrub.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "388572352490011"}], "external_subscription_type"